<% 
  content_for :title, "Relationship Lending - Get a Loan - Find a Banker | Bankmybiz" 
  content_for :description, "Bankmybiz gets a business loan fast by matching and connecting businesses and bankers together." 
  content_for :keywords, "Relationship Lending, Get a Loan, Find a Banker"
%>
<div class="row-fluid">
  <ul class="thumbnails">
    <li class="col-sm-5 col-sm-offset-1">
      <div class="text-center">
        <%= image_tag "michael.jpg", class:"img-circle", width:250 %>
      </div>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Michael Adam, CEO & Founder</h3>
        <p>Prior to launching Bankmybiz, Michael spent over a decade as a commercial lender helping small and middle market businesses achieve success nationwide. His true professional passions are fostering growth, fine-tuning strategy, and building an endless network of COI’s.  Simply, Michael is a business owner who understands that choosing the right financial services partner is critical to a company’s growth and quality of life.  An MBA grad and former middle linebacker at Vanderbilt University, Michael brings his team-player and passionate attitude to BMB’s office everyday. </p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <li class="col-sm-5">
      <div class="text-center">
        <%= image_tag "adam.jpg", class:"img-circle", width:250 %>
      </div>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Adam Braus, CTO</h3>
        <p>After earning his degree in Politics and Linguistics at St. John's College, Adam cut his teeth in the software world working at Epic Systems Corporation as an Implementation Specialist for large enterprise electronic medical record systems. He innovated at Epic, taught himself web design and development in the evenings and weekends, and started two companies before launching into the startup world. Now two years later, he is an experienced entrepreneur and software developer. One of his first startups was in the banking space and he is excited to help lenders and business owners connect on Bankmybiz.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    
    <li class="col-sm-5">
      <div class="text-center">
        <%= image_tag "nathan.jpg", class:"img-circle", width:200 %>
      </div>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Nathan Dauschmidt, COO</h3>
        <p>Nathan was a central banker in Washington for two years before joining the Bankmybiz team. He is a data wrangler with chops in banking and finance. Nathan studied Applied Math and Statistics at Georgetown and has solved problems with data for one Fortune 5 and three Fortune 100 companies around the world. He even worked for the British Government's department for international development. Now Nathan is analyzing the data of Bankmybiz Platform to help businesses and bankers better match each other. Nathan worked a lot for Wall Street when he was at the Central Bank, and now he is happy to be working for Main Street at Bankmybiz. </p>
      </div>
    </li>

    <% if false %>
    <li class="col-sm-5">
      <div class="text-center">
        <%= image_tag "joe.jpg", class:"img-circle", width:200 %>
      </div>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Joseph Zepecki, COO & Co-Founder</h3>
        <p>Joseph worked at the intersection of strategic communications and public policy, including serving as a top communications official at the U.S. Small Business Administration.  In that role, he led the agency’s re-imagination of online services and tools for small businesses.  He believes that the surest path to a strong economy and thriving middle class is supporting the entrepreneurs and small businesses who create two out of every three jobs in the U.S.  A graduate of the University of Wisconsin-Madison (B.A.) and The George Washington University (M.A.), Joseph brings an outside the box perspective to planning and problem solving to BankMyBiz. </p>
